                            <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                What is a recruiter mode job posting and how does it work?
                            </h2>
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                For jobs that are recruiter mode, recruiters can
                                apply to those jobs, out of which a recruiter can
                                be selected by the employer for each job. The applications are then handled
                                by the recruiter to the employer until the hire is
                                finalized.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                How do I decide what type of job posting to do?
                            </h2>
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                There are three categories out of which you can select. If
                                you would like to post jobs for free, you can do so. However, if
                                you are in urgent need or want more thorough selection process and more
                                attention to your jobs, you can select the featured jobs or recruiter mode
                                jobs.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                How is it different from traditional locum agencies?
                            </h2>

                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Our strategy is to minimize the cost of hiring by a greater margin by providing online
                                support and minimizing the unnecessary costs by utilizing a lean model.
                                Through this process, we help connect the providers to the employers directly at a
                                minimum cost.
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                How will it help when I work directly with the candidates without utilizing recruiters?
                            </h2>
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Candidates will be receiving a cashback for each hire up
                                to equal parts of the service fee which is a nominal fee.
                                This is to motivate the candidates to get on board
                                and to help the recruitment process easier while
                                saving money for both the provider and the employer.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingten">
                                Can I post permanent jobs?
                            </h2>
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                We provide a greater pool
